---
title: Baked Turkey and Corn Quesadillas with Pico de Gallo and Lime Crema
description: These mini quesadillas are baked in the oven for convenience but also for the crunchy cheese that melts all over the baking sheet! Dunk it in some lime crema topped with pico for a freshness in each bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/baked-turkey-and-corn-quesadillas-255469f0.jpg
